g.text: This workflow expands on the last
and starts by resizing the images
long time), adding salt and pepper
diffusion filter, and a median filter
It calculates the single to noise ratio
for each using these metanodes and
then joins all of the results together
so it is all in one table
The top path is no filter and we just
call this image 'noisy' as a baseline to
evaluate how if our filters are in fact
